<hw>lime</hw> <pr>(l⟦imac⟧m")</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>having a
yellowish-green color like that of the lime (the fruit).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>limeade</ent>⟦br⟧
